{"tid":1173317,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"非止寒蟬　是直插言論自由核心　言論自由講的是免代價、免恐懼","createTime":"2019-05-27T04:30:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T12:57:25.000Z","uid":47714,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"701e8eb2677c5bc8d8f68b82f2e9ae598944dee4","tid":1173317,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T04:30:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/LungZenoOpen/status/1132179898590621696\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLungZenoOpen%2Fstatus%2F1132179898590621696&d=I3HUAc%2BVzuGSjYFa2O0dWCMX%2BuEjOoKUanh%2Bi4Xf2cM%3D&h=44877f61\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLungZenoOpen%2Fstatus%2F1132179898590621696&h=5f8d9496\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/LungZenoOpen/status/1132179898590621696</a><br />\n<br />\n香港人喜歡自由，但另一方面，很多香港人不會冒風險。張堅庭導演過去97前會出品政治諷刺笑片、表姐你好嘢系列，但他說了他不是烈士，現在不會拍了，他會不會拍可以作為香港有沒有言論自由的標誌。不是寒蟬效應，是直接反言論自由。你犧牲、付代價，一定「自由」，但言論自由講的是免於代價、免於恐懼。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Freedom_of_speech\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FFreedom_of_speech&d=I3HUAc%2BVzuGSjYFa2O0dWCMX%2BuEjOoKUanh%2Bi4Xf2cM%3D&h=70c35715\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Freedom_of_speech</a><br />\n<br />\nFreedom of speech is a principle that supports the freedom of an individual or a community to articulate their opinions and ideas without fear of retaliation, censorship, or legal sanction."},{"pid":"8d3c638f85a1005f37de37915c4c0301685eab05","tid":1173317,"uid":113373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T04:52:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>香港民主終局之戰<br />\n<br />\n【民陣6.9反惡法遊行】 <br />\n日期：6月9日（日）<br />\n集合地點：銅鑼灣東角道<br />\n時間：下午2時30分集合，3時正起步<br />\n遊行路線：銅鑼灣東角道遊行至金鐘添美道<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反對逃犯條例白宮聯署<br />\n-簽完記得確認返電郵<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extraditio